Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.17,0:00:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高坂同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.44,0:00:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.56,0:00:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你来吹独奏部分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是中世古同学 而是由你来 你明白了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.04,0:02:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从大清早直至傍晚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随着暑假的到来练习时间照理变长了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但转眼间就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.39,0:02:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家甚至都觉得还不够的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然发生了那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.48,0:02:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那段 上低音号能一起吹吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:33.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第162小节 和低音大提琴合奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄前酱 能行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.59,0:02:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久美子酱 是这一段
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.57,0:02:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:43.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}重音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.86,0:02:43.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}节奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.45,0:02:43.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}细心！不要走音
